Description_lang: Ulgrax lashes himself to a player and all of their allies within $a1 yards, inflicting $s1 Nature damage divided between all lashed players and $s4 Nature damage every $t4 sec while lashed.Ulgrax then engages in a Carnivorous Contest, pulling all lashed players toward him. The strength of Ulgrax's pull is reduced by the number of lashed players.If fewer than $s3 players are lashed into the Carnivorous Contest, Ulgrax enters an Arrogant Rage.
